<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> February 24, 2026</p>

<p>More Problems is an educational mathematics app. This policy explains how information is handled.</p>

<h2>Local Data</h2>
<p>The app stores high scores and gameplay data locally on your device. This data is not transmitted to a server.</p>

<h2>Advertising</h2>
<p>This app uses Google AdMob to display ads. AdMob may collect device identifiers, usage data, and diagnostic data to serve ads.</p>

<h2>Tracking</h2>
<p>If you allow tracking through Apple's App Tracking Transparency prompt, the app may access the IDFA to deliver personalized ads.</p>

<h2>Your Choices</h2>
<p>You may disable tracking anytime in Settings → Privacy & Security → Tracking.</p>

<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>Email: your@email.com</p>

